{"flatpakAppId":"fr.ipcms.atomes","name":"Atomes","summary":"An atomistic toolbox","description":"\n    <p>Atomes: a toolbox to analyze, to visualize  and to create/edit three-dimensional atomistic models. It offers a workspace that allows to have many projects opened simultaneously. The different projects in the workspace can exchange data:  analysis results, atomic coordinates...</p>\n    <p>Atomes also provides an advanced input preparation system  for further calculations using well known molecular dynamics codes:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Classical MD: DLPOLY and LAMMPS</li>\n      <li>ab-initio MD: CPMD and CP2K</li>\n      <li>QM-MM MD: CPMD and CP2K</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>To prepare the input files for these calculations is likely to be the key, and most complicated step towards MD simulations. Atomes offers a user-friendly assistant to help and guide the scientist step by step to achieve this crucial step.</p>\n  ","developerName":null,"projectLicense":"AGPL-3.0-or-later","homepageUrl":"https://atomes.ipcms.fr/","donationUrl":null,"translateUrl":null,"bugtrackerUrl":"https://github.com/Slookeur/Atomes/issues/new/choose","helpUrl":null,"categories":[{"name":"Education"},{"name":"Science"},{"name":"Chemistry"},{"name":"Physics"}],"downloadFlatpakRefUrl":"atomes","currentReleaseVersion":"1.1.12","currentReleaseDescription":null,"iconDesktopUrl":"http://localhost:7777/repo/appstream/x86_64/icons/128x128/atomes_atomes.png","iconMobileUrl":"http://localhost:7777/repo/appstream/x86_64/icons/128x128/atomes_atomes.png","screenshots":[{"thumbUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/fr/ipcms/atomes/c2d868e4c211ac850e25920a5643f41b/screenshots/image-2_224x126.png","imgMobileUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/fr/ipcms/atomes/c2d868e4c211ac850e25920a5643f41b/screenshots/image-2_1248x702.png","imgDesktopUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/fr/ipcms/atomes/c2d868e4c211ac850e25920a5643f41b/screenshots/image-2_orig.png"},{"thumbUrl":"https://appst